17:53.432 --> 18:08.573
reorganizing and expanding the National Guard of 
New Mexico. Well the president of the School of

18:10.223 --> 18:31.388
Mines was a nice fellow and he was naturally wanted 
if there were any vacancies or anybody any sugar

